The paper deals with machine learning systems and their susceptibility to data poisoning attacks, which are common topics in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer security (cs.CR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of datasets such as MNIST-1-7 and Dogfish suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV), while the use of empirical risk minimization suggests a focus on data science (cs.DS).
